hadiths[114]{hadithnumber,text}:
1837,abu-Usama ne Hisham se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ki qirat suni jo wo raat ko kar raha tha to farmaya : Allah is par raham farmaai ! usne mujhey falan aayat yad dila di jiski tilawat falan sura mein chhod chuka tha.
1838,"Abda aur abu-Muawiya ne Hisham se unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein aik aadmi ki qirat sun rahe they, to aap ne farmaya : Allah is par raham farmaai ! usne mujhey aik aayat yad dila di hai jo mujhey bhulaa di gaee thi."
1839,Imam Malik ne Naafe ke waastey se Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya sahib Quran ( Quran hifz karne waale) ki misal paon bandhey oonton (ke charwaahey ( ki manind (tarah) hai agar us ne unki nigahdaasht ki to wo unhein qaabu mein rakhega aur agar unhein chhod dega to wo chaley jaengey.
1840,Ubaidullah Ayub aur Musa-bin-Aqba sab ne (jin tak sanadon ke mukhtalif silsiley pahunchey ( Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Malik ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki aur Musa-bin-Aqba ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai : jab sahib Quran qiyam karega aur raat din uski qirat karega to wo usey yad rakhega aur jab us (ki qirat (ke sath qiyam nahi karega to wo usey bhool jaeyga
1841,Mansoor ne abu-Waail (Shaqeeq bin Salma) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi bhi insan ke liye intihai na-zeba baat hai ke wo kahey ki main falan-falan aayat bhool gaya hon balke wo bhulwaa diya gaya hai Quran ko yad kartey raho kyonke wo logon ke seenon se door bhaagney mein rassiyon samet bhag janey waley oonton se bhi badh kar hai.
1842,"Aamash ne Shaqiq bin Salma se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : un masaahif . padhi. aur kabhi kaha : Quran . padhi. ke sath ahad ko taza kartey raha karo kyonke wo insanon ke seenon se bhag janey main apne paon ki rassiyon se nikal bhaagney waley oonton se bhi badh kar hai kaha : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai. tum mein se kisi ko ye nahi kehna chahiye ke main falan-falan aayat bhool gaya hun balke usey bhulwaa diya gaya hai."
1843,Abda bin abi Lubaba ne shafeeq bin Salma se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : kisi aadmi ke liye ye bahut buri baat hai ke wo kahey mein falan-falan sura bhool gaya ya falan-falan aayat bhool gaya balke usey bhulwaa diya gaya hai.
1844,Abdullah-bin Baraad Ash-ari aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Barid se unhon-ne abu-Burda se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Quran ki nigahdaasht karo us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! ye bhagney mein paon bandhey oonton se badh kar hai. is hadis ke alfaz ibne- baraad (ki riwayat (ke hain.
1845,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki wo is (farman) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchatey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne (kabhi) kisi cheez par is qadr kaan nahi dhara ( tawajjoh se nahi suna ( jitna kisi khush awaz Nabi (ki awaz ( par kaan dhara jisne achi aawaz se qirat ki.
1846,Yunus aur Amr (bin Haris ( donon ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath ye riwayat ki usmein (  ما اذن لنبي) ke bajaey) ( كما ياذن لنبي ( (jis tarah aik Nabi ke liye kaan dharta hai jo khush aawaz se qirat kar raha ho.) ke alfaz hain
1847,Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ne kaha : Yazeed bin haad ne hamein Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala ne (kabhi) kisi cheez par is tarah kaan nahi dhara jis tarah kisi khush awaz Nabi (ki qirat ( par jab wo buland awaz ke sath khush aawaz se qirat kare.
1848,Umar-bin Malik aur Hewa bin Shureh ne ibne-Haad se isi sanad ke sath bilkul us jaisi riwayat bayan ki aur unhon-ne ( (un Rasulullah ( ) be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( kaha aur) سَمِعَ ( (is ne suna) ka lafz nahi bola.
1849,Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne (kabhi) kisi cheez par is tarah kaan nahi dhara jaisey wo aik Nabi (ki awaz ( par kaan dhartaa hai jo buland awaz ke sath khush aawaz se qirat karta hai.
1850,"Yahya bin Ayub Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur ibne-hijr ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin Jafar ne Muhammad-bin Amr se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne abu-Salma se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki magar ibne- Ayub ne apni riwayat main ( كاذنه (ke bajaey) ( كاذنه ( (jis tarah wo ijazat deta hai) kaha, (is tarah ( ما اذن الله) ka mana hoga Allah Taala ne (baryabi ki) ijazat nahi di."
1851,Hazrat Bareed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais . padhi. ya Ash-ari . ko aal Dawud ki bansuriyon ( khoobsurat aawaazon ( mein se aik bansuri ( khoobsurat awaz ( ata ki gaee hai.
1852,Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : (kya hi khub hota) kash! ! tum mujhey dekhtey jab guzishta raat mein badey inhimaak se tumhari qirat sun raha tha tumhen aal Dawud ki khoobsurat aawaazon mein se aik khoobsurat awaz di gaee hai.
1853,"Abdullah-bin-Idris aur Wakee ne Shoba se aur unhon-ne Muawiya bin Qurra se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin Mughaffal muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka waley saal apne safar main apni sawari par sura fateh ki tilawat farmai aur apni qirat mein awaz ko dohraya . Muawiya ne kaha : agar mujhey ye andesha na hota ke log mere gird jama ho jaeinge to main tumhen Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaisi qirat sunata."
1854,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : Shoba ne hamein Muawiya bin Qurra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fateh Makka ke din apni ontni par) sawar ( sura fateh padhtey huey dekha. (Muaawiya bin Qurra ne) kaha : Hazrat ibne- Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne qirat ki aur is mein tarjee ki, Muawiya ne kaha : agar mujhey logon (ke ikatthey ho janey (ka andesha na hota to main tumharey liye ( qirat ka ( wahi ( tariqa ikhtiyar ( karta jo Hazrat ibne- Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se bayan kya tha."
1855,"Khalid-bin Haris aur Muaz ne kaha : Shoba ne hamein isi sanad ke sath isi tarah ki hadis bayan ki, Khalid-bin Haris ki riwayat mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( sura fateh tilawat kartey huey apni ( sawari par safar kar rahe they."
1856,"abu khaisma ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi sura kahaf ki tilawat kar rhaa tha aur uske paas hi 2 rassiyon mein bandha hua ghoda ( maujood ( tha. to usey aik badli ne dhanp liya, wo badli ghoomti aur qareeb aati gaee aur uska ghoda us se bidakney laga, jab subah hui to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko ye maajra keh sunaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye sakinat ( itminan aur rehmat ( thi jo Quran (ki qirat ( ki bina par) badli ki sura mein) utri."
1857,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : aik aadmi ne sura kahaf ki qirat ki. ghar mein (is waqt) aik chaupaya bhi tha. wo bidakney laga us shakhs ne dekha ke janwar ke uper dhund ya badli thi jo is par chhaai hui hai to usne ye waqia Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya aap ne farmaya : aey shakhs ! padha karo ye to sakeenat thi jo qirat ke waqt utri (ya Quran ki khaatir nazil hui. (
1858,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi aur Abu-Dawud ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna. padhi. aagey donon ( Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi aur Abu-Dawud ( ne pichhli hadis ki tarah zikr kya. albatta itna farq hai ke unhon-ne ( tanaffur ( wo bidakney laga ke bajaey) (تنقز) (wo uchhalney laga) kaha
1859,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) aik raat apne baadey mein qirat kar rahe they ke achcha unka ghoda bidakney laga unhon-ne phir padha wo dobara bidka phir padha wo phir bidka. Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey khof paida hua ke wo (mere betey) Yahya ko raund daalega main uth kar uske paas gaya to achcha chhatri jaisi koi cheez mere sar par thi usmein kuchh charaaghon jaisa tha wo fiza mein buland ho gaee yahan tak ke mujhey nazar aana band ho gaee. kaha : main subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! is beech mein ke kal mein aadhi raat ke waqt apne baadey mein qirat kar raha tha ke achcha mera ghoda bidakney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Huzair! padhtey rehtey. maine kaha : main padhta raha phir us ne dobara uchhal-kood ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Huzair! padhtey rehtey. maine kaha : maine qirat jari rakhi us ne kuchh bidak kar chakkar lagaaney shuru kar diye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Huzair! padhtey rehtey. maine kaha : phir maine chhod diya. ( mera beta) Yahya iske qareeb tha main dar gaya ke wo usey raund dega. to maine chhatri jaisi cheez dekhi usmein charaaghon ki tarah ki cheezein thin wo fizaa mein buland hui yahan tak ke mujhey nazar aani band ho gaee is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Farishtey they jo tumhari qirat sun rahe they aur agar tum padhtey rehtey to log subah ko dekh letey wo unse ojhal na hotey.
1860,abu-Awana ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is momin ki misal jo Quran Majeed ki tilawat karta hai naarangi ki si hai uski khushbu bhi umda hai aur iska zaayqa (bhi khushgawar hai aur us momin ki misal jo Quran Majeed ki tilawat nahi karta khajoor ki si hai uski khushbu nahi hoti jabke iska zaayqa sheereen hai aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran ki tilawat karta hai niyaaz bu jaisi hai uski khushbu umda hai aur zaayqa kadwa hai aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran nahi padhta indrayan ki tarah hai jiski khushbu bhi nahi hoti aur uska zaayqa ( bhi sakht ( kadwaa hai.
1861,Hammam aur Shoba ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis riwayat ki. usmein ye farq hai ke Hammam ki riwayat mein munafiq ki jagah fajir ( badkirdaar (ka lafz hai.
1862,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa (Aamiri) se, unhon-ne Sad bin Hisham se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Quran Majeed ka maahir Quran likhney waley intihai muazzaz aur Allah Taala ke farmanbardar farishton ke sath hoga aur jo insan Quran Majeed padhta hai aur haklata hai. aur wo ( padhna ( uske liye mashaqqat ka baais hai, uske liye 2 ajr hain."
1863,"ibne-abi Adi ne Saeed se riwayat ki, Wakee ne Hisham dustwaai se riwayat ki, un donon ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki albatta Wakee ki hadis mein ye alfaz hain : jo usey padhta hai aur wo is par nagawar hota hai, uske liye 2 ajr hain."
1864,Hammam ne kaha : ham se Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abi (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumharey samney qirat karun. unhon-ne kaha : kya Allah Taala ne aap ke samney mera naam liya ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne mere samney tumhara naam liya. to Hazrat Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey.
1865,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada ko Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : Allah Taala ne hukm diya hai ke main tumharey samney ( لَمْ يَكُنِ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُ‌وا ( ki qirat karun. unhon-ne kaha : aur) Allah Taala ne) aap ke samney mera naam liya hai? aap ne farmaya : haan. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to wo ro diye."
1866,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : Shoba ne hamein Qatada ke hawale se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, padhi. ( aagey pichhli hadis) ki tarah hai."
1867,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Aamash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Ubeda (Salmani) se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mere samney Quran Majeed ki qirat karo. unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya main aapko sunaun , jabke aap par hi to ( Quran Majeed ( nazil hua hai? aap ne farmaya : meri khahish hai ke main usey kisi doosrey se sunoon . to maine sura Nisa ki qirat shuru ki, jab main us aayat par pahuncha : ( فَكَيْفَ إِذَا جِئْنَا مِنْ كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ بِشَهِيدٍ وَجِئْنَا بِكَ عَلَى هَؤُلاَءِ شَهِيدًا (us waqt kya haal hoga, jab ham har ummat mein se aik gawah laaengey aur aapko un par gawah bana kar laaengey . to maine apna sar uthaya , ya mere pahlu mein maujood aadmi ne mujhey thoka diya to maine apna sar uthaya, maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aansu bah rahe they."
1868,"Hannad-bin-sari aur minjab-bin-Haaris Tamimi ne Ali-bin-Mus-hir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, Hannad ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jab aap member par tashrif farma they, mujh se kaha : mujhey Quran sunao."
1869,"Misar ne Amr-bin-Murra se aur unhon-ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : mujhey Quran Majeed sunao. unhon-ne kaha : kya main aapko sunaun jabke ( Quran ( utra hi aap par hai? aap ne farmaya : mujhey achchha lagta hai ke main usey kisi doosrey se sunoon .) Ibrahim ( ne kaha : unhon-ne aap ke samney sura Nisa shuru se us aayat tak sunai : ( فَكَيْفَ إِذَا جِئْنَا مِنْ كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ بِشَهِيدٍ وَجِئْنَا بِكَ عَلَى هَؤُلاَءِ شَهِيدًا (us waqt kya haal hoga, jab ham har ummat mein se aik gawah laaengey aur aapko un par gawah bana kar laaengey . to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is aayat par) ro padey . Misar ne aik dusri sanad se Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye qaul naql kya ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main un par us waqt tak gawah tha jab tak mein unmein raha. Misar ko shak hai. ( ما دمت فيهم ( kaha ya ( ما كنت فيهم ( (jab tak mein unmein tha) kaha,"
1870,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main teiswin mein tha to kuchh logon ne mujhey kaha : hamein Quran Majeed sunaein to maine unhein sura Yusuf sunai. logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye is tarah nahi utri thi. maine kaha : tujh par afsos , Allah ki qism ! maine ye sura Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sunai thi to aap ne mujh se farmaya : tu ney khub qirat ki. isi beech mein ke main us se guftgu kar raha tha to maine us (ke munh ( se sharab ki bo mehsus ki, maine kaha : to sharab bhi peeta hai aur kitabullah ki takzeeb bhi karta hai? to yahan se nahi ja sakta yahan tak ke main tujhey kode lagaaun, phir maine usey had ke taur par kode lagaey ."
1871,Esa-bin-Yonus aur abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki lekin abu-Muawia ki riwayat main ( فقال لي احسنت ( (aap ne mujhey farmaya : tu ney bahut achchha padha (ke alfaz nahi hain.
1872,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se koi shakhs ye pasand karta hai ke jab wo ( bahar se) apne ghar wapas aaey to usmein teen badi farba haamla oontniyan maujood paaey ? ham ne kaha : ji haan ! aap ne farmaya : teen aayatein jinhein tum mein se koi shakhs apni Namaz mein padhta hai. wo uske liye teen bhari bharkam aur motii tazi hamla oontniyon se behtar hain."
1873,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar se nikal kar tashrif laey. ham suffa ( chabootrey ( par maujood they, aap ne farmaya : tum mein se kon pasand karta hai ke rozaana subah Bathaan ya Aqeeq (ki wadi) mein jaey aur wahan se baghair kisi gunah aur qata rehmi ke 2 badey-badey kohanon wali oontniyan laaey? ham ne arz ki, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham sab ko ye baat pasand hai aap ne farmaya : phir tum mein se subah koi shakhs masjid mein kyon nahi jata ke wo Allah ki kitab ki 2 aayatein seekhey ya unki qirat karey to ye uske liye 2 oontniyon (ke husool ( se behtar hai aur ye teen aayatein teen oontniyon se behtar aur char aayatein uske liye char se behtar hain aur) aayaton ki tadaad jo bhi ho ( oonton ki itni tadaad se behtar hai."
1874,"abu-Toba Rabe bin Naafe ne bayan kya ke ham se Muawiya, yani ibne-Salam ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zaid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne abu-Salam se suna, wo kehtey they : mujh se Hazrat abu Amama Bahli (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Quran padha karo kyonke wo qiyamat ke din ashaab Quran (hifz w qirat aur amal karne walon (ka sifarishi bin kar aayega. 2 roshan chamakti hui soortein : al-Baqara aur aale-Imran padha karo kyonke wo qiyamat ke din is tarah aaeingi jaisey wo 2 badal ya 2 saybaan hon ya jaisey wo aik seedh mein udtey parindon ki 2 daarein hon, wo apni sohbat main ( padhney aur amal karne) walon ki taraf se difaa karengi. sura Baqra padha karo kyonke usey hasil karna baaise-barkat aur usey tark karna baaise-hasarat hai aur baatil parast uski taqat nahi rakhtey. Muawiya ne kaha : mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke baatil paraston se saahir ( jadoo gar ( murad hain."
1875,Yahya bin Hassan ne kaha : Muawiya bin Salam ne hamein isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki lekin unhon-ne donon jaghon par) اوكانهما ( ) ya jaisey wo ( ki jagah ( وكانهما ( (aur jaisey wo ( kaha aur Muawiya ka qaul hai ke mujhey ye khabar pahunchi zikr nahi kya.
1876,"Hazrat nawaas bin Samaan Kilabi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : qiyamat ke din Quran aur Quran waley aisey logon ko laya jaeyga jo is par amal kartey they, sura Baqra aur sura Aale-Imran unke aagey-aagey hongi . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un Suraton ke liye teen misaalein din jinko ( sunney ke baad) main ( aaj tak) nahi bhula , aap ne farmaya : jaisey wo 2 badal hain ya 2 kaley saaybaan hain jinke darmyan roshni hai jaisey wo aik seedh mein udney waley parindon ki 2 toliyaan hain, wo apne sahib ( sohbat mein rehney waale) ki taraf se mudaafiat karengi."
1877,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they ke achcha unhon-ne uper se aisi awaz suni jaisi darwaza khulney ki hoti hai to unhon-ne apna sar uper uthaya aur kaha : aasman ka ye darwaza aaj hi khola gaya hai, aaj se pahley kabhi nahi khola gaya, us se aik farishta utra to unhon-ne kaha : ye aik farishta aasman se utra hai ye aaj se pahley kabhi nahi utra , us Farishtey ne salam kya aur (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) kaha : aapko 2 noor milney ki khushkhabri ho jo aap se pahley kisi Nabi ko nahi diye gaey : (eik ( fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) ( sura Fatiha (aur (doosri ( sura Baqra ki aakhiri aayatein . aap un donon mein se koi jumla bhi nahi padhengey magar wo aapko ata kar diya jaeyga."
1878,"Zuhair ne kaha : ham se Mansoor ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Baitullah ke paas Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to maine kaha : mujhey aap ke hawale se sura Baqra ki 2 aayaton ke barey mein hadis pahunchi hai. to unhon-ne kaha : haan, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : sura Baqra ki aakhiri 2 aayatein, jo shakhs raat mein unhein padheyga wo uske liye kafi hongi."
1879,Jarir aur Shoba donon ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki hai.
1880,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Aamash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se, unhon-ne Alqama bin Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne raat ke waqt sura Baqra ki ye aakhiri 2 aayatein padhein , wo uske liye kafi hongi . Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : main khud Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila, wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they, maine unse puchha to unhon-ne mujhey ye riwayat ( seedhey-seedhey ( Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunai."
1881,Esa-bin-Yonus aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Aamash se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
1882,Hafs aur abu-Muawiya ne bhi Aamash se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki hai.
1883,"Muaz bin Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad ghatfaani se, unhon-ne Madaan bin abi Talha Yamari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis ( musalman ( ne sura kahaf ki pehli das aayatein hifz kar lein, usey dajjal ke fitney se mehfooz kar liya gaya."
1884,"Shoba aur Hammam ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki. usmein Shoba ne sura kahaf ki aakhiri ( das ( aayatein kaha hai jabke Hammam ne shuruati ( das ( aayatein kaha hai jis tarah Hisham ki riwayat hai,"
1885,"Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey abu munzir ! kya tum jantey ho kitabullah ki kaun-si aayat, jo tumharey paas hai, sabse azeem hai? kaha : maine kaha : Allah aur us ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zyada jantey hain. aap ne ( dobara ( farmaya : aey abu munzir ! kya tum jantey ho Allah ki kitab ki kaun-si aayat jo tumharey paas hai, sabse azmat wali hai? kaha : maine kaha ( اللَّهُ لَا إِلہ إِلَّا هُوَ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّومُ ( kaha : to aap ne mere seeney par hath maara aur farmaya : Allah ki qism ! abu munzir ! tumhen ye ilm Mubarak ho."
1886,"Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Madaan bin abi Talha se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mein se koi shakhs itna bhi nahi kar sakta ke aik raat mein tehai Quran ki tilawat kar ley ? unhon ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : (koi shakhs) tehai Quran ki tilawat kaisey kar sakta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ( aik tehai Quran ke barabar hai."
1887,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Aban Attaar ne Qatada se usi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki, un donon ( Saeed aur Aban ( ki hadis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne Quran Majeed ke teen ajzaa ( hissey ( kiye hain aur) قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ( ko Quran ke ajzaa mein se aik Juz qarar diya hai."
1888,"Yazeed bin kaisaan ne kaha : hamein abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ikatthey ho jao ! main tumharey samney aik tehai Quran Majeed padhunga. jinhoney jama hona tha wo jama ho gaey phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sura ( قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ( ki qirat farmai, phir ghar mein chaley gaey to ham mein se aik se doosrey ne kaha : mujhey lagta hai aap ke paas shayad aasman se koi aham khabar aai hai. jo aapko andar ley gaee hai. phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( dobara ( bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya : maine tum se kaha tha naa ke main tumhen tehai Quran sunaunga , jaan lo ke ye ( sura ( Quran ke teesrey hissey ke barabar hai."
1889,"abu-Ismail Bashir ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar nikal kar hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : main tumharey samney tehai Quran ki qirat karta hun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ( ) اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ ( padha yahan tak ke usey ( sura ( ko khatm kar diya."
1890,"Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ne, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki parwarish mein thin, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko aik muhim ka ameer bana kar rawana farmaya, wo apne sathiyon ki Namaz mein qirat karta aur) iska ( ikhtitaam ( قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ( se karta tha. jab wo log wapas aaey to unhon-ne is baat ka tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kya. aap ne farmaya : usey poochho , wo aisa kis liye karta tha? sahaba kiram ne puchha to usne jawab diya : isliye ke ye Rehman ( jal w alaa ( ki sifat hai, isliye mujhey is baat se mohabbat hai ke main uski qirat karun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey bata do ! Allah bhi us se mohabbat karta hai."
1891,"bayan (bin Bishr) ne Qais-bin abi Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tumhen malum nahi ke jo aayatein aaj mujh par nazil ki gaee hain un jaisi ( aayatein ( kabhi dekhi tak nahi gain? ( قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَ‌بِّ الْفَلَقِ (aur ( قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَ‌بِّ النَّاسِ ( ."
1892,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair ne bayan kiya, kaha : mere walid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujh se Ismail ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qais se aur unhon-ne Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mujh par aisi aayatein utari gaee hain ke un jaisi (aayatein ( kabhi dekhi tak nahi gain . (yani ( Muawwiz teen .(sura falaq, sura naas)"
1893,"Wakee aur abu-Usama ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat bayan ki, albatta abu-Usama ne Aqba-bin-Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se jo riwayat ki, usmein hai, Aqba-bin-Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke buland martaba sathiyon mein se they."
1894,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ( ibne-Shahab ( Zohri ne Salim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : do chizon ( khoobiyon (ke siwa kisi aur cheez mein hasad ( rashk ( ki gunjaaish nahi : aik wo aadmi jisey Allah Taala ne Quran ki nemat inayat farmai, phir wo din aur raat ki ghadiyon mein iske sath qiyam karta hai. aur doosra wo shakhs jisey Allah ne maal w daulat se nawaza aur wo din aur raat ke oqaat mein usey ( Allah ki raah mein) kharch karta hai."
1895,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do chizon ke ilawa kisi cheez mein hasad ( rashk ( nahi : aik us shakhs se mutaalliq jisey Allah Taala ne ye kitab inayat farmai aur us ne din raat ki ghadiyon mein iske sath qiyam kiya aur doosra wo shakhs jisey Allah Taala ne maal se nawaza aur us ne din raat ke oqaat mein usey sadqa kiya."
1896,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do baton ke siwa kisi cheez mein hasad ( rashk ( nahi kiya ja sakta : aik wo aadmi jisey Allah Taala ne maal diya phir usey is par musallat kar diya ke wo us maal ko haq ki raah mein khuley tour par lootaaey. doosra wo insan jisey Allah Taala ne hikmat ( daanaaii ( ata ki aur wo iske mutabiq (apne aur dusron ke) maamlaat tay karta hai aur uski taleem deta hai.
1897,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se aur unhon-ne Aamir bin Wasila se riwayat ki ke Naafe bin Abdul Haris (Madina aur Makka ke rastey par aik manzil ( Asfan aa kar Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se miley, (wo istiqbaal ke liye aaey (aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) unhein Makka ka aamil banaya kartey they, unhon (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unse puchha ke aap ne ahal wadi , yani Makka ke logon par) bataur naaib ( kisey muqarrar kiya? Naafe ne jawab diya : ibne- Abza ko . unhon-ne puchha ibne- Abza kon hai? kehney lagey : hamarey aazad karda ghulaamon mein se aik hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum ne un par aik aazad karda ghulam ko apna jaa-nasheen bana daala ? to ( Naafe ne) jawab diya : wo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki kitab ko padhney wala hai aur faraaiz ka aalim hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (haan waqei) tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha. Allah Taala is kitab ( Quran (ke zariey bahut se logon ko uncha kar deta hai aur bahuton ko iske zariey se nichey giraata hai."
1898,"Shuaib ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Wasila Lesi ne hadis bayan ki ke Naafe-bin-abdul-haaris-Khuzai ne Asfan (ke maqam ( par Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki. ( aagey ( Zohri se Ibrahim-bin-Sad ki riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
1899,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abdul-Qari se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hisham bin Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko sura furqan us se mukhtalif ( sura mein) padhtey suna jis tarah mein padhta tha. halanke mujhey ( khud ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sura padhai thi, qareeb tha ke main us se jhagda karne mein jald bazi se kaam leta lekin maine usko mohlat di yahan tak ke wo Namaz se farigh ho gaya, phir maine usey galley ki chadar se usey baandha aur kheench kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine usko is tarah sura furqan padhtey huey suna hai jo us se mukhtalif hai jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey wo sura padhai thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey chhod do (aur usey mukhaatab ho kar farmaya) padho. to usne isi tarah padha jis tarah maine usey padhtey huey suna tha. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye sura isi tarah nazil hui hai. phir mujh se kaha : tum padho . maine padha to (is par bhi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye sura isi tarah utri thi. bila shubah ye Quran saat (7) huroof par nazil kya gaya hai. to unmein se jo tumharey liye aasan ho usi ke mutabiq padho ."
1900,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke Miswar-bin-Makhrama aur Abdur-Rehman bin abdul-Qari ne bataya ke un donon ne Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein Hisham bin-Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) ko sura furqan padhtey suna. padhi. aagey usi ki tarah hadis sunai aur ye izafa kya ke qareeb tha ke main is par Namaz hi mein pil padun, maine badi mushkil se sabr kya yahan tak ke usne salam phera."
1901,Mamar ne Zohri se Yunus ki riwayat ki tarah usi ki sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
1902,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujh se Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne mujhey aik harf par) Quran ( padhaayaa , maine unse maraajiat ki, phir main zyada ka taqaza karta raha aur wo mere liye huroof mein izafa kartey gaey yahan tak ke saat (7) harfon tak pahunch gaey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey khabar pahunchi ke padhney ki ye saat (7) sooratein ( saat (7) huroof ( aisey mamley mein hotiin jo (haqeeqat aur mana mein) aik hi rehta, (unki wjah se) halal w haram ke eitibaar se koi ikhtilaf na hota."
1903,hamein Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath khabar di.
1904,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : Ismail-bin-abi Khalid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Esa-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Yala se, unhon-ne apne dada ( Abdur-Rehman ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main masjid mein tha ke aik aadmi dakhil hua, Namaz padhney laga aur us ne jis tarah qirat ki usko maine iske samney naqabile-qabool qarar de diya. phir aik aur aadmi aaya, us ne aisi qirat ki jo iske sathi (pahley aadmi ( ki qirat se mukhtalif thi, jab ham Namaz se farigh huey to ham sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, maine kaha ke is shakhs ne aisi qirat ki jo maine iske samney radd kar di aur doosra aaya to usne apne sathi se bhi alag qirat ki. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya, un donon ne qirat ki. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon ke andaz ki tahseen (taareef) farmai to mere dil mein aap ki takzeeb ( jhutlaaney (ka daaiya (rujhan) us zor se daala gaya jitna us waqt bhi na tha jab main jahiliyat mein tha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh par taarii honey wali us kaifiyat ko dekha to mere seeney mein maara jis se main paseena-paseena ho gaya, jaisey main dar ke aalim mein Allah ko dekh raha hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mere paas hukm bheja gaya ke main Quran aik harf ( qirat ki aik sura ( par padhun. to maine jawaaban darkhaast ki ke meri ummat par aasani farmaaein, to mere paas dobara jawab bheja ke main usey do harfon par padhun . maine phir kaha ke meri ummat ke liye aasani farmaaein, to mere paas teesri baar jawab bheja ke usey saat (7) huroof par padhiye , neez aap ke liye har jawab ke badley jo maine diya aik dua hai jo aap mujh se maangein . maine kaha : aey mere Allah ! meri ummat ko bakhsh de, aey mere Allah ! meri ummat ko bakhsh de. aur teesri dua maine us din ke liye muakhkhar kar li hai jis din tamam makhlooq yahan tak ke Ibrahim bhi meri taraf raaghib hongey."
1905,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke main us masjid mein betha hua tha ke aik aadmi dakhil hua aur Namaz padhi, us ne is tarah qirat ki. ( aagey ( Abdullah-bin-Numair ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
1906,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne Shoba se riwayat ki, unhon-ne ha'km se, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu- ghifaar ke  ( barsati taalaab (ke paas tashrif farma they. kaha : aap ke paas Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aaey aur kaha : Allah Taala ne aapko hukm diya hai ke aap ki ummat aik harf ( qirat ki sura ( par Quran padhey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Allah Taala se iski muaafi ( darguzar (aur uski maghfirat chahta hun meri ummat iski taqat nahi rakhti . phir wo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) dobara aap ke paas aaey aur kaha ke Allah Taala hukm deta hai ke aap ki ummat do harfon par Quran padhey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : main Allah Taala se iski muaafi aur bakhshish mangta hon, meri ummat iski taqat nahi rakhti . phir wo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) teesri baar aap ke paas aaey aur kaha ke Allah Taala hukm deta hai ke aap ki ummat teen harfon par Quran padhey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : main Allah Taala se iski muaafi aur bakhshish mangta hon, meri ummat iski taqat nahi rakhti . phir wo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) chothi martaba aap ke paas aaey aur kaha ke Allah Taala hukm deta hai ke aap ki ummat saat (7) harfon par Quran padhey . wo jis harf par bhi padhengey theek padhengey ."
1907,Muaz Anbari ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
1908,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur ibne-Numair ne Wakee se, unhon-ne Aamash se aur unhon-ne abu-Waail se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi jo naheek-bin-Sanan kahlaataa tha. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman ! aap us kalimey ko kaisey padhtey hain? aap usey ( Alif (ke sath ( مِّن مَّاءٍ غَيْرِ ‌آسِنٍ ( samajhtey hain. ya phir (ya (ke sath ( مِّن مَّاءٍ غَيْرِ‌ياسِنٍ  ( to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se puchha : tum ne is lafz ke siwa tamam Quran Majeed yad kar liya hai? usne kaha : main ( tamam ( mufassal (tafseeli) soortein aik rakaat mein padhta hun. is par Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : sher ki si tez raftaarii ke sath padhtey ho? kuchh log Quran Majeed padhtey hain wo unke gallon se nichey nahi utartaa , lekin jab wo dil mein pahunchtaa aur is mein raasikh hota hai to nafa deta hai. Namaz mein afzal rukoo aur sajdey hain aur main un aik jaisi Suraton ko janta hun jinko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) milaya kartey they, do-do (mila kar) aik rakaat mein padhtey they, phir Abdullah uth kar chaley gaey, is par Alqama bhi unke peechhey andar chaley gaey, phir wapas aaey aur kaha : mujhey unhon-ne wo soortein bata di hain. ibne-Numair ne apni riwayat mein kaha : banu- bajeela ka aik shakhs Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Masood (ke paas aaya, unhon-ne naheek-bin-Sanan nahi kaha."
1909,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik aadmi aaya jisey Nuhaik-bin-Sanan kaha jata tha. (aagey) Wakee ki riwayat ki tarah hai, magar unhon-ne kaha : Alqama Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas (ghar ke andar) haziri diye aaey to ham ne unse kaha : Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se un aapasi milti jalti Suraton ke barey mein poochhein jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik rakaat mein padhtey they. wo unke paas andar chaley gaey aur un Suraton ke barey mein unse poochha, phir hamarey paas tashrif laey aur bataya , wo Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (ke musahaf ( ki tarteeb ke mutabiq mufassal bees soortein hain ( jinhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) das rakaton main ( padhtey they. ("
1910,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : Aamash ne ham se apni isi sanad ke sath un donon ( Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ( ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki. is mein hai. unhon ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main un aik jaisi Suraton ko janta hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) do-do mila kar aik rakaat mein padhtey they, bees soortein das rakaton mein."
1911,"Mehdi bin Memun ne kaha : Wasil ahadab ne hamein abu-Waail se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik din ham subah ki Namaz padhney ke baad Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, ham ne darwazey se (unhein ( salam arz kya, unhon-ne hamein andar aaney ki ijazat di, ham kuchh der darwazey par rukey rahe, itney mein aik bachchi nikli aur kehney lagi : kya aap log andar nahi aaeingey ? ham andar chaley gaey aur wo baithey tasbeehaat padh rahe they, unhon-ne puchha : jab aap logon ko ijazat de di gaee to phir aaney mein kya rukawat thi? ham ne kaha : nahi ( rukawat nahi thi) , albatta ham ne sochaa (ke shayad ( ghar ke kuchh afraad soey huey hun. unhon-ne farmaya : tum ne ibne- Umme- abd ke ghar walon ke mutaalliq ghafalat ka guman kiya? phir dobara tasbeehaat mein mashghool ho gaey yahan tak ke unhon-ne mehsus kya ke suraj nikal aaya hoga to farmaya : aey bachchii ! dekho to ! kya suraj nikal aaya hai? us ne dekha, abhi suraj nahi nikla tha, wo phir tasbeeh ki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaey yahan tak ke phir jab unhon-ne mehsus kya ke suraj tuloo ho gaya hai to kaha aey ladki ! dekho kya suraj tuloo ho gaya hai? us ne dekha to suraj tuloo ho chuka tha, unhon-ne farmaya : Allah ki hamd jisne hamein ye din lota diya. Mehdi ne kaha : mere khayal mein unhon-ne ye bhi kaha, padhi. aur hamarey gunahon ki paadaash mein hamein halaak nahi kya. logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : maine kal raat tamam mufassal Suraton ki tilawat ki, is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tezi se, jis tarah sher tez padhey jatey hain? ham ne aapasii mila kar padhi janey wali Suraton ko suna hai. aur mujhey wo 2-2 soortein yad hain jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) padha kartey they mufassal mein se atthaara soortein aur 2 soortein ( Ha-meem ( wali ."
1912,"Mansoor ne ( abu-Waeil ( Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : banu- bajeela mein se aik aadmi jisey naheek-bin-Sanan kaha jata tha. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : main ( tamam ( mufassal soortein aik rakaat mein padhta hun. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tezi se jaisey sher tezi se padhey jatey hain? mujhey wo aapasii miltii jultii soortein malum hain jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eik-eik rakaat mein do-do karke padhtey they."
1913,"Amr-bin-Murra se riwayat hai, unhon-ne abu-Waail se suna wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke aik aadmi Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : maine aaj raat ( tamam ( mufassal soortein aik rakaat mein padhi hain to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is tez raftaari se jis tarah sher padhey jatey hain? ( phir ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main wo nazaayr (eik jaisi soortein ( pehchanta hun jinko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mila kar padha kartey they unhon-ne mufassal Suraton mein se bees soortein bataein jinhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 milakar aik rakaat mein padhtey they. (un Suraton ki tafseel ke liye dekhiye ( sunan abi Dawud Shahar Ramazan baab takhreeb Quran 1396 ("
1914,"Zuhair ne kaha : ham se Abu-Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik aadmi ko dekha us ne Aswad bin Yazeed (sabeei koofi) se jabke wo masjid mein Quran ki taleem de rahe they. sawal kya : tum is aayat : ( فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ ( ko kaisey padhtey ho? daal padhtey ya zaal? unhon-ne jawab diya : daal padhta hun. maine Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo bata rahe they. ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) مُّدَّكِرٍ‌ ( daal ke sath padhtey suna."
1915,Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se unhon-ne Aswad se unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kalimey ( فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ ( padhtey they (yani daal ke saath).
1916,Aamash ne Ibrahim se aur unhon-ne Alqama (bin Qais koofi) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham Sham (Syria) aaey to hamarey paas Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey aur unhon-ne puchha : kya tum mein se koi aisa hai jo Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat ke mutabiq padhta ho? maine kaha : ji haan main ( padhta hun ( unhon-ne puchha : tum ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye aayat ( وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ ( kis tarah padhtey suna hai. ( maine ( kaha : maine unhein ( وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ Mina و الذَّكَرَ‌وَالْأُنثَىٰ) padhtey suna. unhon-ne kaha : aur maine bhi Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey hi padhtey suna lekin ye log chahtey hain ke main ( وَمَا خَلَقَ الذَّكَرَ‌ وَالْأُنثَىٰ ( padhun mein unke peechhey nahi chalunga. (ibne-Masood aur abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ghaaliban qirat ki us dusri sura se aagah na ho sakey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ne sikhaai thi.)
1917,"Mughira ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Alqama Sham (Syria) aaey aur aik masjid mein dakhil huey usmein Namaz padhi, phir logon ke aik halqey mein ja kar baith gaey itney mein aik sahib aaey to mujhey unke (ird-gird) logon ke ikattha honey aur (unki wjah se) aik khas haiyat ikhtiyar kar leney ka pata chal gaya (is se malum hota tha ke wo khas shakhsiyat hain) ( Alqama ne kaha : wo mere pahlu mein baith gaey. phir farmaya : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) jis tarah padha kartey they kya tumhen wo yad hai? iske baad usi ( pehli hadis ki) tarah bayan kya."
1918,"Ismail bin Ibrahim (ibne-Ulaih) ne Daawood-bin-abii-Hind se unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se mila unhon-ne mujh se puchha : tum kahan se ho? maine kaha : Iraq walon se unhon-ne puchha : unke kon se logon mein se ? maine kaha : ahale-koofa se unhon-ne puchha : kya tum ( Quran Majeed ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat ke mutabiq padhtey ho? maine kaha : ji haan unhon-ne kaha : ( وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ ( padho . maine padha ( وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا يَغْشَىٰ Mina وَالنَّهَارِ‌إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ Mina وَ الذَّكَرَ‌وَالْأُنثَىٰ ( kaha : wo hans padey phir farmaya : maine isi tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko padhtey suna."
1919,"Abdul-Aala ne kaha : ham se Dawud ne Aamir ( Shabi ( se aur unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Sham (Syria) aaya aur Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se mila. padhi.  aagey ibne-Ulaih (Ismail bin Ibrahim ( ki) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
1920,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaze-Asr ke baad suraj ghurub honey tak Namaz padhney se mana farmaya aur subah ke baad suraj tuloo honey tak Namaz se mana farmaya,"
1921,Mansoor ne Qatada se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu Aaliya ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik se zyada sathiyon se suna hai unmein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil hain aur wo mujhey unmein sabse zyada mahboob they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr ke baad suraj tuloo honey tak aur Asr ke baad suraj ghurub honey tak Namaz padhney se mana farmaya hai.
1922,"Shoba, Saeed aur Muaz-bin-Hisham ne apne walid ke waastey se Qatada se isi sanad ke sath ye riwayat bayan ki, albatta Saeed aur Hisham ki hadis mein (namaz fajr ke baad suraj tulu honey tak ke bajaey) subah ke baad suraj chamakney tak ke alfaz hain."
1923,Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : namaze-Asr ke baad koi Namaz nahi yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho jaey aur namaze-Fajr ke baad koi Namaz nahi yahan tak ke suraj tuloo ho jaey.
1924,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs (jaan-bojh kar) tuloo shams aur ghurub shams ke waqt ka irada karke un oqaat mein Namaz na padhey.
1925,"Hisham ke walid Urwa ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apni Namaz ke liye jaan-bojh kar na suraj ke tuloo honey ka irada karo aur na iske ghurub honey ka kyonke suraj shaitan ke 2 seengon ke sath tuloo hota hai."
1926,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab suraj ka kinara namudaar ho jaey to Namaz muakhkhar kar do yahan tak ke wo (suraj) nikal aaey (buland ho jaey) aur jab suraj ka kinara ghurub ho jaey to Namaz muakhkhar kar do yahan tak ke wo (suraj) poori tarah ghayab ho jaey.
1927,"Leis ne khair bin Naeem Hizrami se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Hubaira se, unhon-ne abu Tameem jeeshani se aur unhon-ne abu Basra (Raziallahu anhu) Ghifari se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein makhmas naam ke jagah mein Asr ki Namaz padhai aur farmaya ye Namaz tum se pahley logon ko di gaee (un par farz ki gai) to unhon-ne usey zaaye kar diya, isliye jo bhi uski hifazat karega usey iska 2 guna ajr milega aur uske baad koi Namaz nahi yahan tak ke) iska ( shaahid tuloo ho jaey. shaahid (se murad ( sitaara hai."
1928,"Yazeed bin abi Habib ne khair bin Naeem hizrami se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Hubaira Sabai se. . padhi. aur wo qaabile-bharosa they. unhon-ne abu Tameem jeeshani se aur unhon-ne abu Basra ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Asr ki Namaz padhai. aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah hai."
1929,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke teen wafat hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein roktey they ke ham unmein Namaz padhein ya unmein apne mardon ko qabron mein utaarein : jab suraj chamakta hua tuloo ho raha ho yahan tak ke wo buland ho jaey aur jab do-pahar ko thaharney wala (saaya) thahar jata hai yahan tak ke suraj ( aagey ko) jhuk jaey aur jab suraj ghurub honey ke liye jhuktaa hai yahan tak ke wo (poori tarah) ghurub ho jaey."
1930,"abu Ammar Shaddad-bin-Abdullah aur Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Amama se riwayat ki. Ikrima ne kaha : Shaddad abu Amama aur Wasila (Raziallahu anhu) se mil chuka hai, wo Sham (Syria) ke safar mein Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha aur unki fazeelat aur khoobi ki tareef ki. Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Amr-bin-abasa Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main jab apne jahiliyat ke daur mein tha to (ye baat ( samajhta tha ke log gumrah hain aur jab wo buton ki ibadat kartey hain to kisi ( sachchii ( cheez ( Deen ( par nahi, phir maine Makka ke aik aadmi ke barey mein suna ke wo bahut si baton ki khabar deta hai, main apni sawari par betha aur unke paas aa gaya, us zamaney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chhipey huey they, aap ki qaum (ke log (aap ke khilaf dilair , aur nidar they. main aik lateef tadbeer ikhtiyar karke Makka mein aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se puchha aap kya hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Nabi hun. phir maine puchha : Nabi kya hota hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey Allah ne bheja hai. maine kaha : aapko kya ( paigham ( de kar bheja hai? aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujhey sila rehmii , buton ko todney , Allah Taala ko aik qarar diye, aur uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thahraaney (ka paigham ( de kar bheja hai. maine aap se puchha : aap ke sath is ( Deen ( par aur kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aazad aur aik ghulam. kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us waqt eman laney walon mein se Abu-Bakar aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Mina they. maine kaha : main bhi aap ka muttabea' (pairokaar) hun. farmaya : tum apne aaj kal ke halaat mein aisa karne ki istitaat nahi rakhtey. kya tum mera aur logon ka haal nahi dekhtey ? lekin (in halaat mein) tum apne ghar ki taraf lot jao aur jab mere barey mein suno ke main ghalib aa gaya hon to mere paas aa jana. kaha : to main apne ghar walon ke paas lot gaya aur (baad mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif le gaey main apne ghar hi mein tha, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey. to main bhi khabrein leney aur logon se aap ke halaat poochhney mein lag gaya. yahan tak ke mere paas ahale yasrib (Madina walon ( mein se kuchh log aaey to maine puchha : ye shakhs jo Madina mein aaya hai us ne kya kuchh kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : log tezi se un (ke Deen ( ki taraf badh rahe hain, aap ki qaum ne aapko qatl karna chaha tha lekin wo aisa na kar sakey. is par main Madina aaya aur aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya aap mujhey pehchantey hain? aap ne farmaya : haan tum wahi ho na jo mujh se Makka mein miley they? kaha : to maine kaha : ji haan , aur phir puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey wo (sab ( bataiye jo Allah ne aapko sikhaya hai aur main us se na-waqif hon, mujhey Namaz ke barey mein bataiye . aap ne farmaya : subah ki Namaz padho aur phir Namaz se ruk jao yahan tak ke suraj nikal kar buland ho jaey kyonke wo jab tuloo hota hai to shaitan (apne seengon ko aagey karke yun dikhaataa hai jaisey wo us (ke do seengon ke darmyan tuloo hota hai aur us waqt kaafir us ( suraj ( ko sajda kartey hain, iske baad Namaz padho kyonke Namaz ka mushaahida hota hai aur us mein) Farishtey ( hazir hotey hain yahan tak ke jab neze ka saaya iske sath lag jaey ( suraj bilkul sar par aa jaey) to phir Namaz se ruk jao kyonke us waqt jahannam ko iindhan se bhar kar bhadkaayaa jata hai, phir jab saaya aagey aa jaey ( suraj dhal jaey) to Namaz padho kyonke Namaz ka mushaahida kiya jata hai aur is mein haziri di jati hai yahan tak ke tum Asr se farigh ho jao, phir Namaz se ruk jao yahan tak ke suraj ( poori tarah) ghurub ho jaey kyonke wo shaitan ke do seengon mein ghurub hota hai aur us waqt kaafir iske samney sajda kartey hain. kaha : phir maine puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to wuzu ? mujhey iske barey mein bhi bataiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs bhi wuzu ke liye pani apne qareeb karta hai. phir kulli karta hai aur naak mein pani kheench kar usey jhaadtaa hai to us se iske chehrey , munh , aur naak ke nathnon ke gunah jhad jatey hain, phir jab wo Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq apne chehrey ko dhota hai to laziman iske chehrey ke gunah bhi pani ke sath uski dadhi ke kinaron se gir jatey hain, phir wo apne donon hathon ko kohniyon (ke uper ( tak dhota hai. to laziman iske hathon ke gunah pani ke sath iske poron se gir jatey hain, phir wo sar ka masah karta hai to iske sar ke gunah pani ke sath iske baalon ke aas-paas se zaayel ho jatey hain, phir wo takhnon (ke uper ( tak apne donon qadam dhota hai. to iske donon paon ke gunah pani ke sath iske poron se gir jatey hain, phir agar wo khada hua, Namaz padhi aur Allah ke shaayaan shaan uski hamd w sana aur buzurgi bayan ki aur apna dil Allah ke liye (har qism ke doosrey khayalat w tasawwuraat se) khali kar liya to wo apne gunahon se is tarah nikalta hai jis tarah us waqt tha jis din uski maan ne usey (har qism ke gunahon se paak ( janaa tha. Hazrat Amr-bin-abasa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (eik aur) sahabi Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ko sunai to abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha : aey Amr-bin-abasa (Raziallahu anhu) ! dekh lo tum kya keh rahe ho. aik hi jagah us aadmi ko itna kuchh ata kar diya jata hai ! is par Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ! meri umr badh gaee hai meri haddiyaan narm ho gain hain aur meri maut ka waqt bhi qareeb aa chuka hai aur mujhey koi zarurat nahi ke Allah par jhoot boloon aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jhoot boloon . agar maine is hadis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik , do, teen . yahan tak ke unhon-ne saat (7) baar shumaar kya. padhi. baar na suna hota to main us hadis ko kabhi bayan na karta balke maine to usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us se bhi zyada baar suna hai."
1931,"Wuhaib ne kaha : ham se Abdullah-bin-Taaus ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Taaus ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko waham laahiq hua hai. (ke wo har sura Asr ke baad Namaz padhney ko qaabile saza samajhtey hain) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to is baat se mana farmaya hai ke suraj ke tuloo ya iske ghurub ke waqt Namaz padhney ka irada kya jaey."
1932,"Mamar ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Taaus ke betey se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ke baad 2 rakaat padhni kabhi nahi chhodi thin. kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Namaz ke liye tum jaan-bojh kar suraj ke tuloo aur uske ghurub honey ka irada na karo ke us waqt Namaz padho ."
1933,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb se riwayat hai ke Abdullah-bin-Abbas , Abdur-Rehman bin azhar , Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja aur kaha ke ham sab ki taraf se unhein salam arz karna aur unse Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaat ke barey mein poochhna aur kehna ke hamein khabar mili hai ke aap ye ( 2 rakatein ( padhti hain. jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se ham tak ye khabar pahunchi hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse roka hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main to Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mil kar logon ko unse rokaa karta tha. Kureb ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur un hazraat ne jo paigham dekar mujhey bheja tha maine un tak pahunchaya . unhon-ne jawab diya Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se poochho. main nikal kar un hazraat ke paas lota aur unhein unke jawab se aagah kya. un hazraat ne mujhey wahi paigham de kar Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhej diya jis tarah Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja tha, is par Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke aap un 2 rakaton se roktey they, phir maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye 2 rakatein padhtey huey dekha, haan , aap ne jab ye 2 rakatein padhi thin us waqt aap Asr ki Namaz padh chukey they, phir (asr padh kar) aap ( mere ghar mein) dakhil huey jabke mere paas Ansar ke qabeeley banu- haram ke qabeeley ki kuchh auratein maujood thin, aap ne ye 2 rakatein ada ( karni shuroo) kiin to maine aap ke paas khaadima bheji aur (is se) kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik taraf ja kar khadi ho jao aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz karo ke aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : main aap se sunti rahi hun ke aap (asr ke baad) un 2 rakaton se mana farmatey they aur ab main aapko padhtey huey dekh rahi hoon? agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hath se ishara farmaein to peechhey hat ( kar khadi ho ( jaanaa. us ladki ne aisey hi kya, aap ne hath se ishara farmaya, wo aap se peechhey hat (kar khadi ho) gaee, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to farmaya : aey abu Umayya ( Huzefa bin Mughira makhzoomi) ki beti! tum ne Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaton ke barey mein puchha hai, to (mamla ye hai ke) banu-abdul-Qais ke kuchh afraad apni qaum ke Islam ( laney ki itlaa (ke sath mere paas aaey, aur unhon-ne mujhey Zohar ki baad ki 2 rakaton se mashghool kar diya, ye wahi 2 rakatein hain."
1934,"Yahya bin Ayub, Qutaiba, aur Ali-bin hijr ne Ismail bin Jafar se hadis bayan ki, ibne- Ayub ne kaha : hamein Ismail ne hadis sunai, kaha mujhey Muhammad-bin abi Hurmala ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey abu-Salma ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se un do rakaton ke barey mein puchha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ke baad padhtey they. unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye 2 rakatein (zuhar ke baad) Asr se pahley padhtey they, phir aik din unke padhney se mashghool ho gaey ya unhein bhool gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo Asr ke baad padhin, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein qaaim rakha kyonke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi Namaz (eik baar ( padh letey to usey qaaim rakhtey they. Yahya bin Ayub ne kaha : Ismail ne kaha ( اثبتها ( usey qaaim rakhtey they) se murad hai : aap is par hamesha amal farmatey they."
1935,"Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere yahan Asr ke baad 2 rakatein kabhi nahi chhodein."
1936,"Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad ne apne walid Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : 2 namazein hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere ghar mein unhein raazdari se aur elaniya kabhi tark nahi kya : 2 rakatein fajr se pahley aur 2 rakatein Asr ke baad."
1937,"Abu-Ishaq ne Aswad aur Masruq se riwayat ki, un donon ne kaha : ham Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke barey mein gawahi detey hain ke unhon-ne kaha : koi din jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas hotey they aisa na tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye 2 rakatein na padhi hun. unki murad Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaton se thi."
1938,"Mukhtar-bin-fulful se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Asr ke baad nafl Namaz padhney ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Asr ke baad Namaz padhney par hathon par maartey they aur Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein ham suraj ke ghurub ho janey ke baad namaze-Maghrib se pahley 2 rakatein padhtey they. to maine unse puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye 2 rakatein padhein? unhon-ne kaha : aap hamein padhta dekhtey they aap ne na hamein hukm diya aur na roka."
1939,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Madiney mein hotey they, jab muazzan maghrib ki azan deta to log sutunon ki taraf lapaktey they aur wo 2 rakatein padhtey they yahan tak ke aik musaafir masjid mein aata to un rakaton ko padhney walon ki kasarat dekh kar ye samajhta ke maghrib ki Namaz ho chuki hai."
1940,"Kahmas ne kaha : ham se Abdullah-bin Barida ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har 2 azaanon ( azan aur takbeer (ke darmyan Namaz hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya (aur ( teesri baar farmaya : uske liye jo chaahey."
1941,"Jurairi ne Abdullah-bin Barira se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki misl riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chothi martaba farmaya : uske liye jo chaahey."
1942,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaze-khof padhai, 2 girohon mein se aik ko aik rakaat padhai aur doosra giroh dushman ke samney khada hua tha, phir ye (aap ke sath Namaz padhney waale) palat gaey aur apne sathiyon ki jagah dushman ki taraf rukh karke ja khadey huey aur wo log aa gaey. phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bhi aik rakaat padhai aur uske baad Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam pher diya phir (aap ke baad) unhon-ne bhi apni rakaat mukammal kar li aur unhon-ne bhi dusri rakaat mukammal kar li."
1943,"Fulaih ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Salatul-khauf (ka tariqa ( bayan kartey aur farmatey : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ye Namaz padhi. padhi. ( aagey ( usi ke ham mana hadis hai."
1944,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne jang ke dinon mein se aik din Namaz khof padhai, aik giroh Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz ke liye khada ho gaya aur doosra dushman ke bilmuqabil. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sath khadey honey walon ko aik rakat padha di, phir ye log ( dushman ke muqaabley mein) chaley gaey aur doosrey aa gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bhi aik rakaat padha di, phir un donon girohon ne ( yakey baad doosrey ( eik-eik rakaat ada kar li. ( Naafe ( ne kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar khof us se zyada ho (aur saf bandi mumkin na ho ( to sawari par ya khadey khadey ishara karo aur Namaz padh lo."
1945,"Ata ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaze-khof mein Sharik hua, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari 2 safain banaain, aik saf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey thi (aur dusri unke peechhey (aur dushman hamarey aur qibley ke darmyan tha, Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer ( tahreema ( kahi aur ham sab ne bhi takbeer kahi , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya aur ham sab ne rukoo kya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo se apna sar uthaya aur ham sab ne sar uthaya , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey ke liye jhuk gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se muttasil saf ne bhi sajda kya aur pichhli saf dushman ke madde-muqabil khadi rahi, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 sajdey kar liye aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se muttasil saf ( sajdey karke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saath) khadi ho gaee to pichhli saf sajdey ke liye nichey hui aur phir khadi ho gaee, iske baad pichhli saf aagey aa gaee aur agli saf peechhey chali gaee, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya to ham sab ne rukoo kya. phir aap ne rukoo se apna sar uthaya aur ham sab ne bhi sar uthaya , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se muttasil saf jo pehli rakaat mein peechhey thi, sajdey ke liye nichey chali gaee aur pichhli saf dushman ke muqaabley mein khadi rahi , jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se muttasil saf ne sajda kar liya to pichhli saf sajdey ke liye jhukii . unhon-ne sajdey kiye. phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera aur ham sab ne bhi salam pher diya. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya : jis tarah tumharey muhaafiz ( aajkal ( apne ameeron ki hifazat ke liye kartey hain."
1946,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath juhaina qabeeley ke logon se jang ladi, unhon-ne hamarey sath badi shadeed jang ki jab ham ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi to mushrikon ne kaha : agar ham un par yakbaargi hamla karein to unko kaat kar rakh dein. Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is baat se aagah kar diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein bataya . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un logon ne kaha hai ke abhi unki aik aisi Namaz ka waqt aaney wala hai jo unko unki aulad se bhi zyada pyari hai. jab Asr ka waqt aaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari 2 safain banaain jabke mushrik hamarey aur hamarey qibley ke darmyan they. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer tahreema kahi aur ham ne bhi takbeer kahi , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya aur ham ne bhi rukoo kya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sajda kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath pehli saf ne bhi sajda kya. jab ye hazraat khadey ho gaey to dusri saf walon ne sajdey kiye, phir pehli saf peechhey chali gaee aur dusri aagey badh gaee aur pehli saf ki jagah khadi ho gaee. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer kahi aur ham ne bhi takbeer kahi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo kya aur ham ne bhi rukoo kya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sajda kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( maujooda ( pehli saf ne sajda kya aur dusri khadi rahi. phir jab dusri saf ne sajdey kar liye aur uske baad sab baith gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sab ke sath salam phera . abu-Zubair ne kaha : phir Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne khususi taur par farmaya : jis tarah tumharey ye ameer Namaz padhtey hain."
1947,"Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Saleh bin Khawwaat bin Juber se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sehal-bin-abi-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon ko Namaz khof padhai aur unhein apne peechhey 2 safon mein khada kya aur apne sath (ki saf ( walon ko aik rakaat padhai. phir aap khadey ho gaey aur khadey hi rahe yahan tak ke unse peechhey walon ne aik rakaat padh li, phir ye aagey aagey aur jo unse aagey they peechhey chaley gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik rakaat padhai. phir aap baith gaey yahan tak ke jo peechhey chaley gaey they unhon-ne ( bhi aik aur) rakaat padh li, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera ."
1948,"Yazeed bin Ruman ne Saleh bin khawwat se aur unhon-ne us shakhs se naql kya jisne jang zaatur-Riqaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaaze-khauf padhi thi. ke aik giroh ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saf banai aur doosra giroh dushman ke ru-baru tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sath walon ko aik rakaat padhai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey rahe aur unhon-ne apne taur par (doosri rakaat padh kar) Namaz mukammal kar li aur) salam pher kar) chaley gaey aur dushman ke samney saf band ho gaey aur doosra giroh aa gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo rakaat rehti thi, unko padha di phir baithey rahe aur un logon ne apne taur par) rakaat padh kar) Namaz mukammal kar li to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath salam phera ."
1949,"Aban bin Yazeed ne kaha : ham se Yahya ibne- Kasir ne abu-Salma (bin Abdur-Rehman ( se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (jihad par) aaey. yahan tak ke jab ham (zaatur-Riqaa) (naam ke pahaad) tak pahunchey. kaha : hamari aadat thi ke jab ham kisi ghaney saaey waley darakht tak pahunchtey to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye chhod detey, kaha : aik mushrik aaya jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki talwaar darakht par latki hui thi, us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki talwaar pakad li, usey miyan se nikala aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kehney laga : kya aap mujh se dartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. usne kaha : to phir aapko mujh se kon bachaaeyga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala mujhey tum se mehfooz farmaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ne usey dhamkaya to usne talwaar miyaan mein daal li aur usey latkaaya. iske baad Namaz ke liye azan kahi gaee, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik giroh ko 2 rakaat Namaz padhai , phir wo giroh peechhey chala gaya iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doosrey giroh ko 2 rakatein padhaain. kaha is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki char rakatein huin aur logon ki 2-2 rakatein."
1950,"Muawiya bin Salam ne kaha : mujhey Yahya (bin-abi-kasir) ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke unhein Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaze-khof padhi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik giroh ko do rakatein padhaain, phir doosrey giroh ko 2 rakatein padhaain, is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char rakatein padhein aur har giroh ko 2-2 rakatein padhaain."
